methods.name: GetReplicationDetailActor
methods.comment: Returns the replication details actor for the owner. This must always return a value so lazy load if it doesn't exist.

methods.name: OnBuildableReplicationDetailStateChange
methods.comment: Called when the replication detail actor changes state (i.e. is being interacted with or not).

methods.name: OnReplicationDetailActorCreated
methods.comment: when the replication detail actor has been fully replicated.

methods.name: GetReplicationDetailActorClass
methods.comment: Returns the relevant class type for the replication detail actor. Must inherit from AFGReplicationDetailActor.
